claim: Gwen Stefani is the co-founder of No Doubt along with others.
premise_source_doc_sentence: She is the co-founder and lead vocalist of the band No Doubt that experienced major success after their breakthrough studio album Tragic Kingdom  (  1995  )  along with various successful singles , including `` Just a Girl '' , `` Do n't Speak '' , `` Hey Baby '' , and `` It 's My Life '' .
